metadata.name: SANDSTORM #1
metadata.description:
SANDSTORM #1 is the first piece of the “THE DOOR BETWEEN TWO WORLDS” collection and is a combination of physical art; (the photographs I took during my travels) with digital manipulation among other things as AI algorithms. 

This is a very special & spiritual collection kicking off my NFT journey. 
Every ounce of support is highly appreciate. 

HD downloadable GIF file upon request

x
Zoé
